Package: hurricanegeom
Title: Load, Clean, And Plot Hurricane Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("EL", "Williams", email = "placeholder@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A set of functions to load hurricane data, clean and filter to a specific hurricane and timepoint in the 
  hurricane's track, and plot the hurricane's wind speeds and radial coverage. Additional function included to automate 
  the creation of a base map on which to plot the hurricane data.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
